                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-116" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN STONE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am pot-boy at the Two Brewers, Bunhill-row. I was cleaning my master's windows—I turned and saw the prisoner throw the handkerchief to another boy, who gave it to Mr. Chippendale—I then pur<lb></lb>sued the prisoner and took him—I had not lost sight of him.</p>
